  "body": "![Title](https://cdn.modrinth.com/data/cached_images/c020c4a128129c0559b61acf68f6ec46cf4b7219.png)\n\n  <p align=\"center\">\n<a href=\"https://discord.gg/CdHqyDxMrz\">\n  <img src=\"https://i.pinimg.com/736x/54/b0/5b/54b05bb9f6d4571a9e7c7206d7e2915b.jpg\" \n       alt=\"Discord PixelArt\" \n       width=\"50\">\n</a>\n\n<a href=\"https://www.tiktok.com/@uanderson_test3?_t=8kP3l7qCQ1V&_r=1\">\n  <img src=\"https://i.pinimg.com/736x/07/87/a6/0787a626098d272cd5b9404828fcfcac.jpg\" \n       alt=\"TikTok PixelArt\" \n       width=\"50\">\n</a>\n\n<a href=\"https://youtube.com/@wh_test3?si=5hFPFQdpltcC-8oX\">\n  <img src=\"https://i.pinimg.com/736x/74/97/29/7497291420cdd0ae60e5931d97b54549.jpg\" \n       alt=\"YouTube PixelArt\" \n       width=\"50\">\n</a>\n\n<a href=\"https://www.instagram.com/wanders_test3/profilecard/?igsh=aG85NjQxZHEzdnZ0\">\n  <img src=\"https://i.pinimg.com/736x/cf/df/4b/cfdf4be37a4df24dcf01d9459c200de8.jpg\" \n       alt=\"Instagram PixelArt\" \n       width=\"50\">\n</a>\n\n<a href=\"https://m.twitch.tv/uanderson_test3/home\">\n  <img src=\"https://i.pinimg.com/736x/20/47/ca/2047ca86a5fbadc3d72a4b3222b4914f.jpg\" \n       alt=\"Twitch PixelArt\" \n       width=\"50\">\n</a>\n\n<a href=\"https://x.com/uanderson_teste?t=UDZLCcPgarnHuUMCfI3s5w&s=09\">\n  <img src=\"https://i.pinimg.com/736x/7a/84/57/7a845743f2d491e486b25c2d7c381d3f.jpg\" \n       alt=\"X PixelArt\" \n       width=\"50\">\n</a>\n\n<a href=\"https://open.spotify.com/user/31b6v5kemoxe7cx242v2svghomja?si=oyC1hiNoQYqlJXXraPVu7w\">\n  <img src=\"https://i.pinimg.com/736x/7e/af/5d/7eaf5d0650b600a298d6692e1092f95c.jpg\" \n       alt=\"Spotify PixelArt\" \n       width=\"50\">\n</a>\n\n<a href=\"https://github.com/UandersonTest3\">\n  <img src=\"https://i.pinimg.com/736x/5a/89/1e/5a891eb9dc9d77c6ea517f21de0104ae.jpg\" \n       alt=\"GitHub PixelArt\" \n       width=\"50\">\n</a>\n\nBasically, this resource pack makes all particles emissive without exception.\nThis means that any particle type will glow emissively.\n\nThis can make your game more immersive in some situations or be useful in some occasions, like if you use [REY-Magined](https://modrinth.com/resourcepack/rey-magined-shaders), you can make the particles glow with bloom, giving them an extra touch.\n\n  <p align=\"center\">\n<img src=\"https://cdn.modrinth.com/data/cached_images/146981a830769d2a6661b1d49b33f4cfdf31f817.png\" alt=\"important!\" width=\"275\">\n    \n### *If you find any type of bug or error, report it on my [discord server!](https://discord.gg/CdHqyDxMrz)*",
